{
  "texts": [
    "These datasets overlap with many published benchmarks of learned protein representations.",
    "With the exception of the transcriptomics dataset, where the sequence of codons can be inferred from the transcript, all available datasets reported only amino acid sequences.",
    "To obtain codon information, we mapped UniProt IDs to European Nucleotide Archive entries using UniProtKB 54 and ignored all entries without a match.",
    "We also removed all sequences with unknown nucleotides, containing interstitial stop codons or where the number of nucleotides was not a multiple of three.",
    "Melting temperature."
  ]
}